hifiberry-eeprom (1.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Enhanced error handling with proper exception raising
  * Added retry logic for GPIO initialization with configurable parameters
  * Randomized retry delays to prevent multi-process conflicts
  * Replaced sys.exit() calls with IOError and ImportError exceptions
  * Improved library compatibility for use in other applications
  * Better handling of GPIO access failures and timing issues

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Tue, 01 Jul 2025 16:00:00 +0000

hifiberry-eeprom (1.2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Refactored hateeprom into a proper Python library
  * Added hateeprom Python package with BitbangI2C and HatEEPROM classes
  * Command-line tool now uses the library internally
  * HAT EEPROM parsing with vendor information extraction
  * Support for multiple EEPROM types (24C32, 24C64, 24C128, 24C256)
  * Added info command for displaying HAT information
  * Library can be used by other Python applications
  * Complete API documentation and examples

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Fri, 27 Jun 2025 09:00:00 +0000

hifiberry-eeprom (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Debian package release
  * EEPROM files for HiFiBerry HAT boards
  * Tools for EEPROM compilation and flashing

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 26 Jun 2025 12:00:00 +0000
